<p>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alan-233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5498765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5498765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569477" alt="Alan_233" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5498765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alan-233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5498765); return false;">Alan_233</a></span>（<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dr-a">点此查看更多作品</a>）<br />
后记请移步讨论区</p>
